data.eml:eml: Two new species and new records of caddisflies (Insecta: Trichoptera) from the Far East of Russia

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Arefina, Tatyana I. (2005): Two new species and new records of caddisflies (Insecta: Trichoptera) from the Far East of Russia. Zootaxa 1088: 45-53, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.170519
